1. Install ogr2ogr python module, you can check whether installation has worked by running the following command:
	ogr2ogr --version
2. Make sure the dxf, shp file you want to convert is present in the same folder.
3. Run ogr2ogr -f GML <gml file name> <dxf/shp file name>
4. Open GML file in QGIS to verify that the shape and the attributes have been replicated.
